room_title: Escape room "The Library" by Break Escape in Battle Creek
room_address: 20309 Capital Ave. N. E. Battle Creek, MI 49017
room_description:
Closed Until Spring - 2018.
Your neighbor is an archeologist who has spent time studying the Aztec culture. He has mysteriously disappeared and your team has been contracted to solve the conundrum. I hope you like reading because the answers are in the books.
